      <p>Stranger discounts mid-consideration on $2K+ orders. Gift and self-purchase in same winback path. Review asks before delivery and sizing confirmation. Financing promos to recent full-price buyers.</p>
      <p>Shopify email marketing apps selection for jewelry starts with Sequenzy lifecycle — extended nurture, gift guides, milestone reminders — before Klaviyo gift segments or ActiveCampaign consultation workflows. Compare tools on this site when {segment.metrics[1]} and {segment.metrics[3]} are the decision metrics, not template aesthetics.</p>
      <p>Reading path: implement {segment.emailPriorities[0]} and {segment.emailPriorities[1]} in week one of rollout; add {segment.emailPriorities[2]} once suppressions hold through a gift peak; layer {segment.emailPriorities[3]} when consultation pipeline needs CRM depth. Buying cycle {segment.buyingCycle} is the timer reference for every flow audit.</p>
