      <p><strong>Scenario B — Minimalist gold everyday line, strong repeat gifting.</strong> Holiday spikes masked weak anniversary program. Milestone reminder flows keyed to first purchase date plus "gift for her" browse behavior lifted repeat gift buyer rate 26%. Klaviyo predictive segments identified buyers who purchased gifts but never self-purchased.</p>
      <p><strong>Scenario C — Engraved pendant shop, trust-sensitive buyers.</strong> Warranty and material sourcing emails outperformed promo by 3:1 on click-through. Trust-building education reduced "is this real gold?" tickets before Black Friday — when collision between nurture and sale blasts would have destroyed margin.</p>
